{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fd1861abc6","title":"中共中央关于许世友、赵紫阳等同志职务任免的通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7f3e81d142","index":0,"year":1974,"month":4,"day":4,"articleId":"fd1861abc6"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"634a5de908","name":"广东文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"c2f8307fbd","name":"许世友","type":"人物"},{"id":"f584ca053e","name":"赵紫阳","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"44636823ba","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于许世友、赵紫阳等同志职务任免的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"fd1861abc6"},{"id":"c0e9c52112","type":"subtitle","text":"中共中央通知","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"fd1861abc6"},{"id":"c4cb4cd774","type":"appellation","text":"广东省委、广州军区党委：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"fd1861abc6"},{"id":"706395e1b0","type":"paragraph","text":"中央决定许世友同志任广州军区党委第一书记[1]，韦国清同志任广州军区[党委]第二书记，赵紫阳同志任广东省委第一书记、广东省革委会主任[2]、广州军区政委、广东省军区第一政委。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"fd1861abc6"},{"id":"ab0b043905","type":"paragraph","text":"调孔石泉同志回广州军区工作，仍任广州军区政委、广州军区党委书记。免去孔石泉同志广东省委书记、广东省革委会第一副主任职务。免去任思忠[同志]省军区政委职务，由中央军委另行分配工作。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"fd1861abc6"},{"id":"a09433090c","type":"paragraph","text":" 中共中央  中央军委一九七四年四月四日","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"fd1861abc6"},{"id":"c4fb242717","type":"paragraph","text":"[1] 从1973年12月至此前，该职务空缺。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"fd1861abc6"},{"id":"9a712634c8","type":"paragraph","text":"[2] 此前系丁盛任广东省革委会主任职务。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"fd1861abc6"}],"page":{"id":"47de8490a0","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"fd1861abc6","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}